'''39大道車站'''（{{lang-en|39th Avenue station}}），又稱「39大道-荷蘭溪車站」（{{lang-en|39th Avenue–Dutch Kills station}}），是[[紐約地鐵|紐約地鐵]][[BMT阿斯托利亞線|BMT阿斯托利亞線]]的一個慢車[[地鐵站|地鐵站]]，位於[[皇后區|皇后區]][[長島市_(皇后區)|長島市]]39大道及31街交界，設有[[紐約地鐵N線|N線]]（任何時候停站）與[[紐約地鐵W線|W線]]（僅平日停站）列車服務。
== 歷史 ==
此站在1917年2月1日連同阿斯托利亞線一同啟用，起初是[[跨區捷運公司|IRT]]的路線，現為[[IRT法拉盛線|IRT法拉盛線]]的[[IRT皇后區線|皇后區線]]分支，列車來往[[大中央車站_(IRT法拉盛線)|大中央]]至阿斯托利亞<ref name="AstoriaExtension2">{{cite web|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/54438288/?terms=ditmars+boulevard+subway+station|title=First Train Runs On Elevated Line to Astoria Section|date=February 1, 1917|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|accessdate=June 29, 2015|newspaper=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|archive-date=2019-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905063043/https://www.newspapers.com/image/54438288/?terms=ditmars+boulevard+subway+station|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":02">{{Cite book|url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=mdp.39015016416920;view=1up;seq=23|title=Annual report. 1916-1917.|last=|first=|publisher=Interborough Rapid Transit Company|year=1917|isbn=|location=New York|pages=|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929005320/https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=mdp.39015016416920;view=1up;seq=23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1917年7月23日，由{{link-en|IRT第二大道線|IRT Second Avenue Line}}分支的{{link-en|高架鐵路|Elevated railway}}[[皇后區大橋|皇后區大橋]]啟用。當時所有往皇后區廣場的高架列車使用阿斯托利亞線，而所有地鐵列車使用可樂娜線，後來改為梅花間竹地往不同支線開行列車<ref name=":02" /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1917/07/22/archives/subway-link-over-queensboro-bridge.html|title=Subway Link Over Queensboro Bridge|date=July 22, 1917|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=December 18, 2011|page=31|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821081742/https://www.nytimes.com/1917/07/22/archives/subway-link-over-queensboro-bridge.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站在1923年4月8日起開始有[[布魯克林-曼哈頓運輸股份有限公司|BMT]]使用高架列車作接駁<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1923/04/08/archives/hylan-tells-how-he-would-relieve-subways-in-60-days-start-and-quit.html|title=Additional Subway Service to Borough of Queens|date=April 8, 1923|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=December 18, 2011|page=RE1|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821081743/https://www.nytimes.com/1923/04/08/archives/hylan-tells-how-he-would-relieve-subways-in-60-days-start-and-quit.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1949年10月17日，阿斯托利亞線成為只有BMT的路線，因為[[皇后區廣場車站|皇后區廣場車站]]的軌道已經固定，阿斯托利亞線的月台更被削走以容許BMT列車在上營運。起初服務由平日運行的「布萊頓慢車」（[[BMT_1|BMT 1]]）以及任何時段運行的「百老匯-第四大道慢車」（[[BMT_2|BMT 2]]）提供<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1949/10/15/archives/direct-subway-runs-to-flushing-astoria.html|title=Direct Subway Runs to Flushing, Astoria|date=October 15, 1949|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=December 18, 2011|page=17|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821081746/https://www.nytimes.com/1949/10/15/archives/direct-subway-runs-to-flushing-astoria.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 車站翻新 ===
此站月台與阿斯托利亞線其餘6個車站在1950年延長至{{Convert|610|feet|meters}}以容許10節列車<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=98j0AAAAMAAJ&q=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&dq=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi4kuGRubnXAhWB0iYKHV8WCLM4ChDoAQgsMAE|title=Bulletin|last=Association|first=General Contractors|date=1950|language=en|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918192324/https://books.google.com/books?id=98j0AAAAMAAJ&q=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&dq=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi4kuGRubnXAhWB0iYKHV8WCLM4ChDoAQgsMAE|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Rp|23}}。總花費86.3萬美元。路線的訊號需要修改以考慮延長的月台<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TrocAQAAMAAJ&q=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&dq=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiT49zIubnXAhWKTCYKHeGVASwQ6AEIKDAA|title=Proceedings ...|last=Transportation|first=New York (N Y. ) Board of|date=1950|language=en|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918192332/https://books.google.com/books?id=TrocAQAAMAAJ&q=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&dq=%22astoria+line%22+platform+extensions&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiT49zIubnXAhWKTCYKHeGVASwQ6AEIKDAA|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Rp|633, 729}}。

在2015－2019年[[大都會運輸署|MTA]]資金計劃，車站與其他三十個紐約地鐵車站進行翻新，並關閉幾個月。更新內容包括蜂窩服務、Wi-Fi、充電站、改善指示牌、改善車站燈光<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gothamist.com/2016/01/08/subway_facelift_shutdown.php|title=MTA Will Completely Close 30 Subway Stations For Months-Long "Revamp"|publisher=Gothamist|accessdate=July 18, 2016|date=January 8, 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801200338/http://gothamist.com/2016/01/08/subway_facelift_shutdown.php|archivedate=2016年8月1日}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.governor.ny.gov/sites/governor.ny.gov/files/atoms/files/MTAStations.pdf|title=MTAStations|last=|first=|date=|website=governor.ny.gov|publisher=Government of the State of New York|access-date=July 18, 2016|archive-date=2019-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102093442/https://www.governor.ny.gov/sites/governor.ny.gov/files/atoms/files/MTAStations.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二批次的翻新合約包括30大道、[[百老匯車站_(BMT阿斯托利亞線)|百老匯]]、[[36大道車站|36大道]]以及[[39大道車站_(BMT阿斯托利亞線)|39大道車站]]在2017年4月14日批出予[[斯堪卡|斯堪卡]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/mta/news/books/pdf/170424_1315_CPOC.pdf|title=Capital Program Oversight Committee Meeting|last=|first=|date=April 2017|website=mta.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|page=17|access-date=April 24, 2017|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005195730/http://web.mta.info/mta/news/books/pdf/170424_1315_CPOC.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站與百老匯車站一同在2018年7月2日關閉，並在2019年1月28日重開<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mta.info/press-release/nyc-transit/broadway-39-av-nw-stations-undergo-extensive-repairs-renovations|title=Broadway & 39 Av NW Stations to Undergo Extensive Repairs & Renovations|last=|first=|date=June 8, 2018|website=www.mta.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141944/http://www.mta.info/press-release/nyc-transit/broadway-39-av-nw-stations-undergo-extensive-repairs-renovations|archive-date=2018-06-12|dead-url=no|access-date=June 8, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/Bway_39Av/index.htm|title=Broadway and 39 Av stations will temporarily close for extensive renovation All times beginning 5 AM, July 2, until February 2019|last=|first=|date=June 2018|website=web.mta.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823092922/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/Bway_39Av/index.htm|archive-date=2019-08-23|dead-url=no|access-date=June 18, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://travel.mtanyct.info/serviceadvisory/routeStatusResult.aspx?tag=ALL&date=1/28/2019&time=&method=getstatus4|title=Planned Service Changes for: Monday, January 28, 2019|last=|first=|date=|website=travel.mtanyct.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129001529/http://travel.mtanyct.info/serviceadvisory/routeStatusResult.aspx?tag=ALL&date=1%2F28%2F2019&time=&method=getstatus4|archive-date=2019-01-29|dead-url=no|access-date=January 28, 2019}}</ref>。在荷蘭溪公民協會的要求下安裝的新站名牌顯示為「39大道-荷蘭溪」<ref>{{cite web | last=Goff | first=Liz | title=39th Ave. Train Station To Be Co-Named ‘Dutch Kills’ | website=Queens Gazette | date=January 9, 2019 | url=http://m.qgazette.com/news/2019-01-09/Features/39th_Ave_Train_Station_To_Be_CoNamed_Dutch_Kills.html | access-date=February 7, 2019 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209123933/http://m.qgazette.com/news/2019-01-09/Features/39th_Ave_Train_Station_To_Be_CoNamed_Dutch_Kills.html | archive-date=2019-02-09 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=A Long Island City train station receives a brand-new name | website=QNS.com | date=January 2, 2019 | url=https://qns.com/story/2019/01/02/to-the-surprise-of-everyone-a-long-island-city-train-station-receives-a-brand-new-name/ | access-date=February 7, 2019 | archive-date=2020-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812031057/https://qns.com/story/2019/01/02/to-the-surprise-of-everyone-a-long-is